**Summary:** This Japanese documentation explains how to leverage predictive cohorts for targeted marketing campaigns, covering three campaign types (inclusion criteria, dynamic pricing, content personalization), campaign setup with cohort synchronization to destinations like Facebook/Google/Braze/Iterable, and measuring campaign results using lift analysis and relative lift comparisons between variant and control groups.

